net.cnri.repository.search

Interface Query

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AttributeQuery, BooleanQuery, ElementAttributeQuery, MatchAllObjectsQuery, RawQuery, SyncingRepository.ModifiedSinceLastSyncQuery

    public interface Query
    A query for a repository. A query is defined by which objects match the query.

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      <T> T accept(QueryVisitor<T> visitor)
      Returns the result of applying a QueryVisitor to this query.

    • Method Detail

      • accept

        <T> T accept(QueryVisitor<T> visitor)
      throws RepositoryException
        Returns the result of applying a QueryVisitor to this query. A QueryVisitor implementation will return different results based on the runtime type of the query. This allows the emulation of structural pattern matching over possible Query types.
        Parameters:
        visitor - the visitor
        Returns:
        the result of the visit
        Throws:
        RepositoryException
